text: bis denas mansas quod Anglice diciturTwenti hide.
Ærest endlang þe fer to Alorbroke endlang Alorbrokes to Wodeford.

Of Wodeford to Streteford of Streteford to Meredich vp of Meredich out to bilham þat hit comet to langforlang suthward þanen to Hengrave of Hengrave to cefelandgrave þanen to abbanberghe to þan orputten to þe fer ist sone.
